Pub/Sub over http using COMET endpoint for the Nodester PaaS
  Running on: http://pubsub.nodester.com/
  
* open a terminal and type:
      curl http://pubsub.nodester.com/lmao
* open a second term and type:
      curl -d 'body=sup' http://pubsub.nodester.com/lmao

Watch first terminal in amazement. 
Bear in mind that depending on the message size, it can take some time to be rendered on a browser, but will be retrieved by javascript.

